  1326	<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  1327	<div class="section">
  1328	  <h1><span class="sec-num">§13</span> Risk Analysis and Mitigations</h1>
  1329	
  1330	  <table>
  1331	    <thead>
  1332	      <tr>
  1333	        <th>Risk</th>
  1334	        <th>Likelihood</th>
  1335	        <th>Impact</th>
  1336	        <th>Mitigation</th>
  1337	      </tr>
  1338	    </thead>
  1339	    <tbody>
  1340	      <tr>
  1341	        <td>Cold-start shows no improvement over baseline StyleVector</td>
  1342	        <td>Low–Medium</td>
  1343	        <td>High</td>
  1344	        <td>Frame null result as a valid finding. Analyze which cluster configurations work and why. A rigorous negative result is still publishable and defensible in a chalk talk.</td>
  1345	      </tr>
  1346	      <tr>
  1347	        <td>Kaggle session timeout during activation extraction</td>
  1348	        <td>High</td>
  1349	        <td>Medium</td>
  1350	        <td>Save activations in batches of 100 to disk. Resume from last checkpoint on next session.</td>
  1351	      </tr>
  1352	      <tr>
  1353	        <td>Insufficient sparse authors after filtering All The News</td>
  1354	        <td>Low</td>
  1355	        <td>High</td>
