<div class="section">
  <h1><span class="sec-num">§12</span> Tool Stack and Rationale</h1>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Tool</th>
        <th>Role</th>
        <th>Rationale</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>LLaMA-2-7B-chat</strong></td>
        <td>Core language model for activation extraction and steered generation</td>
        <td>Same model used in the StyleVector paper. Results are directly comparable.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Gemini API (Flash)</strong></td>
        <td>Style-agnostic headline generation (Step 1 of StyleVector)</td>
        <td>Fast, free-tiered, and robust. Paper shows generic model choice has minimal impact on results.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Kaggle T4 GPU</strong></td>
        <td>Heavy compute: activation extraction, style vector training</td>
        <td>Free 16GB VRAM, sufficient for 4-bit quantized LLaMA-2-7B. Personal GPU (4GB) is insufficient.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Lightning AI</strong></td>
        <td>Overflow compute when Kaggle sessions expire</td>
        <td>~50 credits available. Used for long-running jobs that exceed Kaggle's session limit.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>FastAPI</strong></td>
        <td>Backend REST API</td>
        <td>Fast, modern, Pydantic-native. Ideal for ML inference serving.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Next.js 14</strong></td>
        <td>Frontend application</td>
        <td>React-based with server components. Good Tailwind support. Auto-deploys on Vercel.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>HuggingFace Spaces</strong></td>
        <td>Backend deployment</td>
        <td>Free tier, Docker-native, publicly accessible URL. Perfect for academic demos.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>GitHub Actions</strong></td>
        <td>CI/CD pipeline</td>
        <td>Native GitHub integration, free for public repos, supports secret management for HF token.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Claude Code</strong></td>
        <td>Code writing, debugging, refactoring throughout project</td>
        <td>Best available tool for Python/FastAPI/Next.js code generation and debugging.</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>


