          <div class="timeline-title">Repository, Environment & Dataset Download</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">Project repository created with full folder structure. All the News dataset downloaded and author filtering pipeline built. CI/CD skeleton in place from day one.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 2</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">Data</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Scraping, Cleaning & Author Splits</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">Indian news scraped from TOI and Hindustan Times. Both datasets cleaned, unified into a single schema, and split into rich/sparse author groups chronologically.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 3</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">Generation</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Style-Agnostic Headline Generation via Gemini</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">For every article in the training set, Gemini API generates a neutral headline. Results saved to disk — this step is only run once.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 4</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">ML Core</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Activation Extraction & Style Vector Computation</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">LLaMA-2-7B run on Kaggle GPU. Hidden activations extracted for every article-headline pair. Rich-author style vectors computed and saved.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 5</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">Novel Contribution</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Clustering & Cold-Start Interpolation</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">Style vectors clustered using K-means. Cold-start interpolation implemented and validated. Alpha hyperparameter sweep conducted to find the optimal blend ratio.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 6</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">Evaluation</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Full Experiment Results</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">All four methods evaluated on all metrics. Result tables finalized. This is the core academic deliverable of the project.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 7</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">Application</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Backend API + Frontend Development</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">FastAPI backend built and tested locally. Next.js frontend developed with all three screens. End-to-end flow tested locally before deployment.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-row timeline-last">
        <div class="timeline-week">Week 8</div>
        <div class="timeline-line"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><div class="timeline-connector"></div></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-phase">Deployment</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Docker, CI/CD, Live Deployment & README</div>
          <div class="timeline-detail">Application containerized and deployed to HuggingFace Spaces. Full CI/CD pipeline active. Comprehensive README written. Project submitted via GitHub Classroom.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
  <div>Cold-Start StyleVector · Course Project · NLP & Full-Stack ML</div>
  <div>Dataset: Public · Deployment: HuggingFace Spaces + Vercel · Stack: Python · FastAPI · Next.js</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
